{"about_the_game":"Block Strategy is an RTS Base Defence roguelite with a fully destructible world. <br><br>While trying to escape an overwhelming enemy force you warp through space to safety and must rebuild your base. Defeat enemies to receive a choice of upgrades and resources to allow you to specialise your units and base in different ways and defend from waves of enemies.<br><br>Gather enough strength (and fuel for your reactor) to travel to the enemy base and defeat them for good.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/title_-_build_bases.png?t=1727694770\" /><br>Place buildings to provide extra units, generate additional resources over time, power your base, or defend against waves of enemies. Enemies attack at specified intervals, giving you time to explore and gather resources before hunkering down to defend.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/placing_buildings_2.gif?t=1727694770\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/title_-_upgrade_units.png?t=1727694770\" /><br>Create up to 6 hero units which can level-up and be augmented with different weapons and abilities. These allow units to specialise, becoming more of a damage dealer, healer, tank and more.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/robot_costumes.gif?t=1727694770\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/title_-_explore_defeat_bosses.png?t=1727694770\" /><br>Explore the world , fight bosses and complete events to be rewarded with resources, buildings and upgrades.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2642070/extras/fighting_good_fps_8.gif?t=1727694770\" /